freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Fatigue, muscle and joint pain, woke up this morning, my head was clear, no muscle or joint pain. Its been a horrible week but overnight this is the best I have felt since the first Covid shot.I feel I can now return to my life as it was,
I am just so tired, some days stiff joints.  At last gastric problems seem to have settled down.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Seems to have brought on a colitis episode
